  "detailed_description": "The Cruise 2 is a top down 2D space themed roguelike shooter where the players dodges hail storms of bullets while defeating enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers can try out different player classes with different abilities and passives that can be customized to find new ways to eliminate the enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll sorts of different enemy types will also appear throughout the stages of the game, they all do different things and will need different tactics to defeat them. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDifferent bosses will also spawn at the end of stages, it requires more skill to dodge the bosses' attacks. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAllies will also spawn and help you take down some enemies, different allies will do different things, and will support you in different ways. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is still being developed, so expect new content to come out once in a while.",
  "about_the_game": "The Cruise 2 is a top down 2D space themed roguelike shooter where the players dodges hail storms of bullets while defeating enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers can try out different player classes with different abilities and passives that can be customized to find new ways to eliminate the enemies. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll sorts of different enemy types will also appear throughout the stages of the game, they all do different things and will need different tactics to defeat them. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDifferent bosses will also spawn at the end of stages, it requires more skill to dodge the bosses' attacks. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAllies will also spawn and help you take down some enemies, different allies will do different things, and will support you in different ways. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game is still being developed, so expect new content to come out once in a while.",
